hms.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Bod Pod History</b></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Research first began on the development of the Bod Pod in 1990.  The work began based on financial assistance via Small Business Innovative Research grants.  These grants were awarded by the National Institutes of Health (NIH) from the United States.  The NIH is the most respected and prestigious health organization in the world.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since the Bod Pod was formally introduced in 1994, it has been heavily used, researched and validated.  Literally dozens and dozens of research studies, scientific reports, white papers and peer reviewed journal articles have been published in trade journals and medical publications.  Each has validated the accuracy, reliability and the ease-of-use of the Bod Pod and its proprietary Air Displacement Plethysmograph technology.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The vast majority of researchers and medical professionals now consider the Bod Pod to be </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“The Gold</span></i> <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Standard”</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in body composition testing and measurement.</span>\r\n<h3><b>Bod Pod Research and Science Reports</b></h3>\r\n&nbsp;','About the Bod Pod','','inherit','closed','closed','','28-revision-v1','','','2015-09-04 12:34:26','2015-09-04 17:34:26','',28,'http://musclemetrics.zone/28-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(72,3,'2008-09-04 08:08:10','2008-09-04 13:08:10','The NFL\'s New York Jets have purchased a BOD POD® Gold Standard Body Composition Tracking System from Life Measurement, Inc. The Jets become the 16th NFL franchise to incorporate the BOD POD® device to measure players\' body composition and metabolism.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<h3>NEW YORK (PRWEB) SEPTEMBER 3, 2008</h3>\r\n<div id=\"contentWrap\">\r\n<div class=\"newsItem\">\r\n<p class=\"responsiveNews\">The NFL\'s New York Jets have purchased a BOD POD® Gold Standard Body Composition Tracking System from Life Measurement, Inc. The Jets become the 16th NFL franchise to incorporate the BOD POD® device to measure players\' body composition and metabolism.</p>\r\n<p class=\"responsiveNews\">Born from university research, the BOD POD® has become the practical gold standard for fast, accurate, and safe body composition analysis in the elite athletic community. NFL, collegiate, MLB, Olympic, and premier athletic programs are utilizing the BOD POD to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"releaseul\">\r\n	<li>Accurately assess lean body mass and fat mass of players</li>\r\n	<li>Track the effectiveness of nutrition, rehabilitation, and training programs;</li>\r\n	<li>Develop individual, sport, and/or position-specific body composition goals and ranges;</li>\r\n	<li>Assess caloric requirements through Resting Metabolic Rate (RMR) and Total Energy Expenditure (TEE) analysis;</li>\r\n	<li>Provide athletes with additional motivation and knowledge on body health;</li>\r\n	<li>Accommodate a wide range of subjects (size, race, and gender).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[tt_btn link=\"http://www.prweb.com/releases/2008/9/prweb1280054.htm\" target=\"_blank\"]Read the full story @ PRWEB[/tt_btn]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','New York Jets become the 16th NFL team to utilize a BOD POD','','publish','open','open','','new-york-jets-become-the-16th-nfl-team-to-utilize-a-bod-pod','','','2015-09-09 11:33:24','2015-09-09 16:33:24','',0,'http://musclemetrics.zone/?p=72',0,'post','',0),(73,3,'2015-09-04 12:42:51','2015-09-04 17:42:51','&nbsp;\r\n<div id=\"contentWrap\">\r\n<div class=\"newsItem\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"Befit_BodyTxt\">The NFL\'s New York Jets become the 16th NFL team to utilize a BOD POD for body composition and metabolic assessment.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n[tt_btn link=\"http://www.prweb.com/releases/2008/9/prweb1280054.htm\" target=\"_blank\"]Read the full story[/tt_btn]','New York Jets become the 16th NF